{"tid":570220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完黑豹之後萌生咗一個睇法","createTime":"2018-02-23T12:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T13:56:01.000Z","uid":164163,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64bf90f6ad0046723388d63d4f6a2cc12923bc73","tid":570220,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"如果為連登仔起返個連登國嘅話 有冇巴絲會想住喺度?<br />\n<br />\n嗰度會係一個烏托邦 雖然無民主 但大家唔駛為任何嘢煩惱 我嘅一班團隊會大家一一解決所有生活上嘅難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政治方面 唔會再有左派右派 因為脫離咗阿爺嘅管治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n溝仔/女方面 我會為大家配對一個你值得擁有嘅伴侶 當然你愈付出得多喺自己身上 就愈可以得到更高質素嘅伴侶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/201359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F201359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f019f369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[gold]LIHKGIAN FOREVERRRRR/gold]</span>"},{"pid":"0cbc6bceb3286e7fd9ace04dc8b5f1fbf4481b0e","tid":570220,"uid":33095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"訓醒啦"},{"pid":"4d6a8eae72ab435b319a6f40d3c6e2208838b68a","tid":570220,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">LIHKGIAN FOREVERRRRR</span></span>"},{"pid":"242e34d1e2a55f039d2b23937ed905d841a3409e","tid":570220,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c